 true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1498564800.0} {"text": "World of Guns: Gun Disassembly Que vas a esperar de este ''juego'' simple como es su maquinaria nada m√°s, para ser m√°s claro consiste en desarmar y armar las armas de fuego y probarlas nada m√°s, as√≠ es, solo haces eso con todo este ''juego'' o software como a ti te guste llamarlo ( NOTA: de ahora en adelante le dir√© software ), pero quiz√°s el software se vuelva repetitivo porque tarde o temprano se vuelve porque al final es eso desarmar, armar y probar armas y ya est√°. ¬øse recomienda este software? La respuesta es... depende de que te guste porque es eso lo que dije con anterioridad yo no dir√© nada solo pondr√© recomendado porque soy alguien interesado en el tema de armas de fuego. (¬øALGUIEN PIENSA QUE ESTE SOFTWARE ES COMO ESAS DEMOS TECNICAS QUE MUESTRAN EN LAS TARJETAS GRAFICAS‚Ä¶ ALGUIEN?). :/", "appid": "262410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198272338045", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1522843200.0} {"text": "c cool", "appid": "512470", "steamid": "profiles/76561198038737182", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589457600.0} {"text": "Pog", "appid": "1286830", "steamid": "profiles/76561198127495899", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601812800.0} {"text": ".", "appid": "249990", "steamid": "profiles/76561198063417065", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530619200.0} {"text": "Slutt √• les rewievs√• mine for svarte!", "appid": "255710", "steamid": "profiles/76561198033182774", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511438400.0} {"text": "Fun and at times really challenging game, bummer that it has some achievements tied to DLCs, but it was really enjoyable for all the 35+hrs I'd played it. Achievements are kind of fun to hunt in this and the GFX is not terrible. Just a great racing game I would recommend, if you can get it for under 15‚Ç¨ I think it's worth it.", "appid": "44350", "steamid": "profiles/76561198111138111", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1591617600.0} {"text": "or let me say this; When we think of old video games, our subconscious mind goes to childhood or adolescence games. Games that we dig into our memories to see that makeup half of our memories. Definitely one of those games is Tekken, which, with its release on Sony's first console, was able to attract a lot of fans and become one of the serious competitors for Mortal Kombat. Years pass, and these two veteran rivals have risen alongside each other. Two fighting games with different shapes and icons for fans, one targeting the East style and the other the West style. Of course, the presence of other fighting games such as the Injustice series has led Mortal Kombat's production team to target a wider audience. when that has been released, it was time for Tekken 7 to show itself. The main question here is, was Tekken 7 as good as it looks? \"Children begin their work with the love and affection of their parents, soon after judging them and finally forgiving infrequently.\" << BEFORE READING: next paragraph contains spoiler >> The STORY of the game is narrated according to this quote. Where Kazuya Mishima's hatred of his father is well portrayed. On the other hand, the story of Tekken 7 will show the audience what caused the death of Kazumi by Heihachi and why Kazuya hates his father. The story of the game cannot be considered the end of the Mishima family's war and conflict, but it closes the case of the events between father and son. The story is told in the language of a narrator. A journalist who has started researching Mishima Zaybatso and G company and intends to find the reason for the destruction of his hometown. Tekken 7 includes a main story and a side story, in the main story, the events are narrated in three different branches, and finally, they are in the same direction and are well summarized. On the one hand, Kazuya, who intends to destroy Heihachi and avenge his childhood and his mother's. Akuma, on the other hand, enters the field. Someone who has promised Kazumi in the past to destroy Heihachi. Now that these characters are taking revenge, the Tex Force team is trying to find Jin Kazama and bring him back to Mishima zaibatsu <> in a fighting game, gameplay plays the most important role. That the game can satisfy the audience well in the combat system or other areas is the most important factor that any fighting game should consider. Therefore, Tekken 7 has shown itself well in this section. Most fighting games try to modernize, however, Tekken 7 is well-balanced between a modern fighting game and a classic fighting game. The presence of old combos, the animation style of the fights, and the movement of the players are all reminiscent of the previous versions, which are available here with new elements. The most important thing to consider is how to use Rage Art. In fact, Rage Arts are the special combinations of players that you can use. As your health bar approaches critical conditions, a red halo appears around you, signaling the activation of Rage Art. Now you can use serious buttons to inflict serious damage on your opponent. Other gameplay features that give the game a fresh look is Power Crush, which allows you to hit your opponent when you're being hit and stop their combo. The slow-motion feature has also been added to this version since the sixth version to once again illustrate the sensitivity of all-time kicks. Now suppose that all these combat capabilities and features will find their true meaning when they being used in great combos and continue hitting when your opponent is between heaven and earth and don't let your opponent get a chance to hit. You can also use the walls of the game environment to combine your shots and do more damage to the opponent. The availability of these features has not only not made the gameplay crowded, but has made the fights more precise; Find out exactly when you need to use your Rage Art or Rage Move, when to hit and when to hit your opponent harder, or when to use a combination of environments combo. Aside from storytelling, gameplay in both offline and online includes a variety of combat modes, each with its own strengths and weaknesses. In the offline section, the arcade mode of the game includes fights with AI. When I entered this section, I expected to see several fights for each character, but for each character, there are only five fights, among which Heihachi and Kazumi that are present in all the fights. In other words, you only have three fights in which the AI ‚Äã‚Äãcharacters are random and new. After a while, the arcade mode will make you very tired and you may not go to this section anymore. But no matter how weak the arcade mode, Treasure Battle mode compensates for it. In this part, you will fight your favorite characters with other characters in the game, and then you will have a series of special competitions with Heihachi, Jin, Akuma, and Kazuya. There are two things you can never get tired of in treasure mode. The first is the greater number of fights than the arcade section, and the second and most important is the availability of chests at the end and beginning of each match. Now, another difference between the arcade mode and the Treasure Battle mode is the game's AI (artificial intelligence). In the story section, you can determine the artificial intelligence and the difficulty yourself, but in this section, there are no such options. Therefore, we see the rank-based difficulty. The online part is another pillar of the Tekken 7 gameplay; Where players from all over the world come together to test their skills. The online part of the game consists of three different modes. The first mode of Player Match that you will compete with other players or you can create a lobby yourself so that the players can connect to you and play. In both Ranked and Player Match modes, you can hardly find an opponent, and if it is found, your ping is so different from your opponent that you are all over the game during the game, or you can't connect to the opponent's server and player at all. Now the only part of the tournament that you can easily play with others (of course, if we factor in ping problems). Of course, sometimes during the tournament, the host may lose and leave the game. Then you will leave the tournament and all your efforts will be wasted, and unfortunately, there is no specific punishment for the violators. One thing that has always stood out in the Tekken series is the game's graphics and game design. Thanks to the Unreal Engine 4 graphics engine, the development team has tried to strike a balance between classic and modern in the game's graphics. The struggles and designs of the environment and the characters all promise a classic Tekken game. Apart from that, Tekken 7's combat environments have a good variety, and some of them include two combat places that, if your fight lasts, you will see that the place you're fighting in, will be ruined by your hits and opponent falls and enter another part of the place. With all these interpretations, Tekken 7 came back after years of waiting for the fans of this series to make good moments for them again. An original oriental fighting game that has been around for about 20 years and has tried to add new elements to its audience experiences. Apparently, the game never intends to make big changes, and that could be good news for fans.", "appid": "389730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198315680994", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "49", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593950400.0} {"text": "Great Game to Customize your Steam Profile!"