200000.0} {"text": "9 —Ä–∞–∑–µ_–±–∞_–Ω–Ω—ã—Ö –∫–ª–∞–≤–∏–∞—Ç—É—Ä –∏–∑ 10", "appid": "657200", "steamid": "profiles/76561198357469522", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561377600.0} {"text": "This a great game to play with friends (at the time of writing I only play regularly with 1 friend but that's going up to 2 soon). If you're looking for something with gameplay a little like L4D2, but themes from Alien, Star Troopers, burly dwarves and casual alcoholism, this may be the game for you and your friends. For those concerned by the Early Access tag (if it still applies), don't worry about that too much - after 2 years in public testing and development, the content in this game has grown explosively and it pretty much a reflection of the final product by this point. There's only 4 classes to play, 8 weapons to master and 8 tools to help you do it, but if you think that this means you'll be finished with DRG's content in an afternoon you'd be sorely wrong. The sheer difference in gameplay, from one build to another, makes the grind to complete that build feel appropriately spaced and appropriately rewarding. Single player is available, but while it's kinda fun to make the drone do all the more boring work for you, multiplayer is where this game is at.", "appid": "548430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198178517897", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1575547200.0} {"text": "A fun, fast-paced 2D action game.", "appid": "280010", "steamid": "profiles/76561198086313488", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1443787200.0} {"text": "Fun detective game", "appid": "945360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198106244516", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1604577600.0} {"text": "Da", "appid": "311690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198383228376", "voted_up": true, "v