ry easy to play with friends. The new , although a big laggy sometimes based on the \"host\" connection, works absolutely fine and adds extra fun to the trip. The price may be a bit high for now, but that's understandable for a game in EA that needs players who are willing to share opinions and help the game growing process. After playing many hours, discussing and discovering the secrets and new content that doesn't was in the first game, my conclusion is that Risk of Rain 2, after a great week on its debut, has conquered almost everyone that played it. With 6 playable characters at the moment, it can fit a very large variety of playstyles. And the devs shall be making it even greater with new content and bug-fixing updates.", "appid": "632360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198098440825", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1554292800.0} {"text": "nicu gamu", "appid": "280160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198087351365", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542974400.0} {"text": "Jogo bom , as vezes da vontade de enfiar a merreta no c* e rodar de tanta raiva.", "appid": "240720", "steamid": "profiles/76561198428648325", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "30", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593086400.0} {"text": "It may be the most random steam game since they removed deadpool from the platform. the powers, which you will be unlocking progressively and satisfactorily, give you absolute mobility over the city. So much freedom that you prefer to kick the city from end to end trying uracans, forcing civilians to dance dupstep and proving worthy explosions of the same magnitude as chernobyl. Contains a system branches evolved for literally anything in the game. ‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô• fun with a million references to pop culture and an impressive soundtrack that fits perfectly with the situations that occur in the game. Despite its graphics