06400.0} {"text": "Relax To Play", "appid": "562220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198334313564", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1481976000.0} {"text": "Eight hours straight directly when I came home from work. This is a gem of a game allready in EA and I can't even start about how I look forward to play this as it grows both in content and quality. Runs amazingly good and loading times are not bad at least on my computer", "appid": "261550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198023130923", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1585569600.0} {"text": "Imagine CIV5, but constant combat, less about the city building and tech advancing, more about the straight up combat", "appid": "489630", "steamid": "profiles/76561198027714922", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1605528000.0} {"text": "Experience a game unlike anything else. This unique masterpiece is a perfect fit for people enjoying sarcastical and controversial views on (American) society. The story is about daily errands tasked by your \"lovely\" wife and the gameplay only gets as violent as you let to provoke yourself. You can finish the game with zero kills or nuke the whole town to Hell while pissing (!) on people until they puke. xD It's really not a game for fun killers taking it seriously and that's why it gets every rating from 0% to 100%. Even the developers are mucking about themselves by putting their studio ingame and using the restroom as an office. :D The \"missions\" have a great variety, from trivial stuff like getting milk from the supermarket or bringing back a book to the library up to pissing on your Dad's grave and running around with a Gimp Suit downtown. Other activities include visiting a Taliban terror camp or Uncle Dave's drug farm. Apart from the story you can also just run around and enjoy exploring the town like a free-roam sandbox game. The game was orginal released back in 2003 but thanks to Greenlight got a second spring on Steam, a new add-on called \"Lost Paradise\" and still (!!) receives regular updates from the developers - after more than 15 years. It's a true Labour of Love; it's proudly banned in Australia, New Zealand and Malaysia; it's funny and totally insane; it uses cats as silencer and counts the number of kicked in doors; it has 69 achievements (the number is NOT a coincidence, you get it, right?) and even featured in Black Eyed Peas \"Where's the Love?\" music video. As you can see the impact of this game is as unique as itself and worth a try!", "appid": "223470", "steamid": "profiles/76561197968240913", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "27", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511438400.0} {"text": "–ü–æ–ª—å—â–∞ –º–æ–∂–µ –≤ –ö–æ—Å–º–æ—Å!! –Ø –°–î–ï–õ–ê–õ –≠–¢–û))))))))", "appid": "512033", "steamid": "profiles/76561197993962137", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": "14", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1538395200.0} {"text": "Memes... It's just nature going it's own way.", "appid": "235460", "steamid": "profiles/76561198110793727", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "Sehr gutes Spiel am anfang kaum erfolgserlebnisse aber wenn man sich reingefunden hat macht es mega Spa√ü :) Edit: Stand 2016 und es ist immernoch extrem geil! :)", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198105130828", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1434801600.0} {"text": "ùòéùò≥ùò¶ùò¢ùòµ ùò®ùò¢ùòÆùò¶", "appid": "960090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198449852486", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1578398400.0} {"text": "very good", "appid": "304930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198087658963", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1417780800.0} {"text": "What a bunch of entitled crybabies. Bad korean translation? So what? Is your \"thumbs down\" justified? Of course not. It's like not getting a PHD because you made a couple spelling mistakes. I am ashamed that this game had such a toxic korean fanbase. Not only koreans jumped on this bangwagon. This game is one of the best I've played IN YEARS, and many of you say the same. So why the thumbs down? You want developers to change translation by lowering rating below 50% DURING A SUMMBER SALE? This is one of the biggest opportunities for them to earn money to continue development! And their game is no longer being recomended because of its rating! You can ignore them, you can boycott them, but changing your review like that is such a bowel movement I would totally spit in your face if I met you in person.", "appid": "262060", "steamid": "profiles/76561198013137662", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530014400.0} {"text": "‡∏™‡∏ô‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏Å‡∏Å‡∏Å ‡∏¢‡∏¥‡πà‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏•‡πà‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏¢‡∏¥‡πà‡∏á‡∏™‡∏ô‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏Å‡∏Å ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏î‡∏µ ‡πÄ‡∏™‡∏µ‡∏¢‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏Å‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏î‡∏¢‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏Å ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏Ñ‡∏Ñ ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ ‡∏à‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏•‡∏≥‡∏ö‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏Å;w;", "appid": "251170", "steamid": "profiles/76561198117148944", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1496404800.0} {"text": "- 24 hours I don't know how to start. This game and 'Just Cause 3' were my very first steam purchases. This reminds me some nostalgic memoriesüòç. I don't know why I underestimated this game. Whatever, THIEF (2014) is the reboot of the classic 'Thief' series. The game is set in 'The City', a dark fantasy world inspired by Victorian, Gothic, and steampunk aesthetics. You control Garrett, a master thief who has exceptional thieving skills...Ok let's get to the PROS and CONS>> - - I cannot remember another. If I find, I will add here. - Story - 7/10 Gameplay - 8/10 Level Design - 9-10 Overall - 8/10 Most of my friends have this their library..But if you don't have, buy this during a sale... Thanks for reading....Some information is collected from wikipedia", "appid": "239160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198394232524", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "27", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1558353600.0} {"text": "After finished the mission solo, I must say, It's one of those cool missions on the series, There were several shortcut paths that I said to myself \"man, wish I had a chem kit\" while I chose to carried a wire cutter. Some of the shortcuts are really resourceful in this one. The map design is also remarkable, the lighting is great in many dark and dim areas. The fact that the area of the mission takes place in the nearby area of Hell or High Water giving you the nostalgic feeling and also making the world more believable. I finished it with heat level full in the first time and It felt like I john wicked the way through the mission (you know... a church and all) All in all a total fun episode to start a second season. It's not too hard to do it alone, and it's not too easy or short to make you feel lacking. I'll have to replay it again and again, cause it's that good!", "appid": "987170", "steamid": "profiles/76561198063418879", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543492800.0} {"text": "Even more fun with Left 4 Dead characters. Better get it from sales or you will be left for dead.", "appid": "301640", "steamid": "profiles/76561198000460264", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1462622400.0} {"text": "Game is pretty solid, lots of variety with weapons, warframes, and the builds you put on them. Game is grindy and you can play this game for free and easily find a way to trade and obtain some valuable in game currency.", "appid": "230410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198042553093", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543233600.0} {"text": "Este juego va a poner tu ansiedad hasta el techo. Un juego de terror que me sorprendi√≥ gratamente, esperaba el t√≠pico juego indie que te mete el screamer en cuanto puede, el t√≠pico juego de terror que no trasmite nada. Y me termin√© llevando una buena sorpresa, el s√≥tano de Dios plantea un argumento muy interesante, una reflexi√≥n muy curiosa, da mucho que pensar. Y tiene una forma de transmitir terror muy inteligente, para empezar, no es el t√≠pico juego en el que ten√©s que rajar del monstruo, de hecho no pod√©s morir, pero esto no hace que te sientas inmortal... En todo momento te sent√≠s d√©bil. Tambi√©n tengo que agregar que la idea que tiene el s√≥tano de Dios como premisa es bastante interesante y llama la atenci√≥n nada m√°s empezar a jugar. Lo recomiendo much√≠simo si quieren pasar miedo... el s√≥tano de Dios los va a ser sentir muy inc√≥modos.", "appid": "753930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198276140352", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589457600.0} {"text": "gg", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198815434175", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1518868800.0} {"text": "I played this game for over 100+ hours and it was pretty fun. I played casual but, then it got boring. So i started playing csgo!", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198308490265", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1493467200.0} {"text": "–ö–æ–¥–ª–∞ –î–ê–£–ù–û–í! –ù–æ —è –õ–Æ–ë–õ–Æ —ç—Ç—É –∫–æ–¥–ª—É –î–ê–£–ù–û–í <3 <3 <3", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198150056766", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574424000.0} {"text": "Anlatmaya gerek yok :D