Ω–∞–∫–æ–º–∏–ª–∞—Å—å —Å –¥–µ–≤—á–æ–Ω–∫–æ–π!!! –°–ø–∞—Å–∏–±–æ —Ç–µ–±–µ, Don't starve together! –ú—ã –∑–∞–º–µ—á–∞—Ç–µ–ª—å–Ω–æ –ø—Ä–æ–≤–æ–¥–∏–º –≤—Ä–µ–º—è –≤–º–µ—Å—Ç–µ, –æ–Ω–∞ –º–Ω–µ –ø–æ –≤—Å–µ–º –ø–æ–º–æ–≥–∞–µ—Ç, –≤–º–µ—Å—Ç–µ –º—ã —Å–∏–ª–∞! AMIN", "appid": "322330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198369102843", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511438400.0} {"text": ":ok_ay:", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198280048688", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542974400.0} {"text": "not bad", "appid": "252850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198161502088", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1480248000.0} {"text": "Ïª§Î≤å Ï£ΩÏù¥Îäî Í≤åÏûÑ", "appid": "220200", "steamid": "profiles/76561198256150102", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1563537600.0} {"text": "A pesar de no ser una obra maestra de Telltale como otras, es un gran juego. Creo que su mejor punto es c√≥mo consigue sumergirte de golpe en Bruce Wayne y hacerte sentir como √©l absolutamente. La sensaci√≥n de ser Batman y tener que lidiar con sus decisiones es realmente buena. La historia no est√° mal. Probadlo, que si os gusta lleg√°is a tiempo de la segunda temporada.", "appid": "498240", "steamid": "profiles/76561198018671613", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1507204800.0} {"text": "Come on I NEED IT KNOW !!! LUL :D MORE MOREEE MOREEEEEEEE ^^", "appid": "1113410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198373784349", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1581681600.0} {"text": "An absolutely lovely indie game. Great for light-gaming even for hardcore gamers. One of the best games out there tbh.", "appid": "250900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198139183648", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1591358400.0} {"text": "It's rare that a developer goes from make a adult game about crime with very adult themes. To making a game about a high school kid who moves to a school for child delinquents and socially challenged kids, but in a lot of ways Bully is like a GTA. For example Bully is a giant open world with stuff to collect, bike races to do, arcade games to play, and much more to just kind of find.The mission structure is very similar to GTA, you do a bunch of work for one of the factions;like the jocks or the nerds, and the more the more you do work for one faction it can effect your standing with others. Which in turn can effect the way some of the people treat you at school. The combat is very similar but instead of machine guns and rocket launches. Your playing with slingshots and stink bombs. There are also a lot of things that are different about Bully that really makes it feel like your in high school it feel very structured, but that's not a bad thing at all. Like you have classes two times a day everyday until you pass the highest level of that class, and of you don't go the prefects or any adult of authority. All the classes have there own perks like one of the classes shows you where all the collectibles, and unlike the protagonists in GTA jimmy is 15 and needs his sleep so if your out past 2 you just pass out on the spot which can make some night missions feel a little too time restrictive. The story starts you out in a car ride with you and your mom and what seems to be your new stepdad. They then drop you off in the front of Bullyworth academy where you meet the principle and some of the teacher, but the fun starts to come in when you go to your dorm room and meet your new friend Gary, who is a sociopath, i don't know how else to put it.You soon start to become manipulated by him, and you two soon go your separate ways and you start to see less and less of him. You then start to do work for the other factions of the school. Playing Bully it kind of puts you back and makes you think about your time in high school, I know the archetypes aren't as plain and simple as they are in Bully but it does a great job of boiling a lot of the high school experience down to a 20 hour game. Then there are a few technical issues with bully I didn't really have too many other then the game crash on me a couple of times, and that just sucks after that happened for the first time a started saving much more frequently. I can't really say definitely how the game will turn out for you, but it didn't seem to bad. From my experience with it. Over all the game is well made but parts of it just seem kind of repetitive and broken;overall though I think it's a great game.", "appid": "12200", "steamid": "profiles/76561198139909925", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1418126400.0} {"text": "Fun but challenging game.", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561197996062617", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "very good", "appid": "431960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198422980383", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "–û—á–µ–Ω—å –∏–Ω—Ç–µ—Ä–µ—Å–Ω–∞—è –∑–∞—Ç—è–≥–∏–≤–∞—é—â–∞—è –∏–≥—Ä–∞, –¥–æ—Å—Ç–æ–π–Ω–æ–µ —Ä–∞–∑–≤–∏—Ç–∏–µ —Å–µ—Ä–∏–∏ –∏ –ø–µ—Ä–µ—Ö–æ–¥ –Ω–∞ –Ω–æ–≤—ã–π —Ñ–æ—Ä–º–∞—Ç –∏–≥—Ä—ã. –í—Å—ë –≤ –Ω–∞–ª–∏—á–∏–∏: –≤—ã–∂–∏–≤–∞–Ω–∏–µ –≤ –µ6–µ–Ω—è—Ö –ª—É–∏–∑–∏–∞–Ω—Å–∫–∏—Ö –±–æ–ª–æ—Ç, —Å–±–æ—Ä –ø—Ä–µ–¥–º–µ—Ç–æ–≤, –∑–∞–≥–∞–¥–∫–∏, –∫—Ä–∞—Ñ—Ç, –±–µ–∫—Ç—Ä–µ–∫–∏–Ω–≥ –ø–æ –ª–æ–∫–∞—Ü–∏–∏ (–∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä—ã–π –∞–±—Å–æ–ª—é—Ç–Ω–æ –Ω–µ –Ω–∞–ø—Ä—è–≥–∞–µ—Ç), –∏–Ω—Ç–µ—Ä–µ—Å–Ω—ã–µ –±–æ—Å—Å—ã –∏ –æ—á–µ–Ω—å –∫—Ä—É—Ç–æ–π —Å—é–∂–µ—Ç. –ü—Ä–æ—à–µ–ª –∏–≥—Ä—É 3 —Ä–∞–∑–∞ –ø–æ–¥—Ä—è–¥ –Ω–∞ –≤—Å–µ—Ö —Å–ª–æ–∂–Ω–æ—Å—Ç—è—Ö, —á—Ç–æ–±—ã –æ—Ç–∫—Ä—ã—Ç—å –≤—Å–µ unlockables –∑–∞ –ø—Ä–æ—Ö–æ–∂–¥–µ–Ω–∏–µ. –ò –µ—â–µ –≤ –∏–≥—Ä–µ –ø—Ä–æ—Å—Ç–æ –æ—á—É–º–∏—Ç–µ–ª—å–Ω—ã–µ DLC, –∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä—ã–µ –æ—á–µ–Ω—å –≥—Ä–∞–º–æ—Ç–Ω–æ –¥–æ–ø–æ–ª–Ω—è—é—Ç –ª–∏–Ω–∏—é –æ—Å–Ω–æ–≤–Ω–æ–≥–æ —Å—é–∂–µ—Ç–∞.", "appid": "418370", "steamid": "profiles/76561198087021864", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "26", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599739200.0} {"text": "Voy a ser lo mas crudo posible. Si sos de los que disfrutan de la tension en todo momento este juego es para vos, ya que a partir del dia 13 con todas las precauciones posibles, empiezan a venir oleadas y oleadas, lo que hace que la partida se de por acabada. Es un gran juego con increible historia, construcciones realistas y divertidas, vistas alucinantes y canibales sabrosos :) Te dare un par de consejos: 1) cuando tales un arbol, destruye el Junco, si no lo haces las patrullas de canibales pensaran que hay algo malo en esa zona y seran mas frecuentes. 2) NO ATAQUES A LOS CANIBALES SI ELLOS NO TE ATACAN PRIMERO, ya que ser agresivo con los canibales influye en el juego y hace mas frecuentes los avistamientos de canibales y mutantes. 3) no te enfoques tanto en tu base, si bien es algo importante para tener un lugar donde almacenar tus recrsos y pasar la noche, acostumbra a visitar cuevas, ya que estas son fundamentales en la historia y te dan los objetos mas importantes. 4) crear una casa del arbol es fundamental, ya que hace que los canibales no puedan acceder (tienen autismo y no entienden las cuerdas los mogolicos). 5) estudia la guia del juego, los canibales no son tan retrasados como parecen, tienen sistemas, patrullas, bases, comunicacion entre ellos, tipos de canibales y demas. Por no hablar de los mutantes, esos si que hay que estudiarlos con la guia (Por si no queda claro con Guia me refiero a la de Google, no dentro del juego). 6) Cuando estes en una cueva agachate siempre y solo prendas la antorcha o el encendedor en momentos sumamente importes, ya que estos te hacen muy visibles. 7) Si llega a pasar que los canibales te empezaron a atacar, matalos a todos, no dejes ni uno vivo ya que esto hara que al dia siguiente vengan mas 8) con un hacha poder desmembrar a los canibales y comerte sus extremidades, yuummi :) 9) Te recomiendo hacer tu base en un lugar cerca de un lago y lejos de bases canibales (hay una app en la Play Store que te muestra el mapa con todas las leyendas).", "appid": "242760", "steamid": "profiles/76561198448900398", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "33", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1580990400.0} {"text": "I bought this to make profit from the cards :^]", "appid": "368990", "steamid": "profiles/76561198007948566", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1434110400.0} {"text": "Desde que salio Half-Life en el a√±o 1998, este juego sigue siendo un exito total en 2020. Me llen√≥ de buenos recuerdos jugarlo cuando lo conoc√≠. Empez√© a jugar Half-Life y sus mods en el a√±o 2018, en mi colegio deseo poder jugarlo con mis amigos al igual que el Counter-Strike. Este juego para mi sigue siendo famoso. Se llen√≥ varios memes sobre este juego que me han hecho reir demaciado, Hasta tambi√©n. Hago, realizo y trabajo modificaciones acerca de Half-Life. Gracias Valve por haber creado este maravilloso juego. Muchaas graciaaas :D.", "appid": "70", "steamid": "profiles/76561199012362486", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1579089600.0} {"text": "A good one handed time waster, Covid eat your heat out.", "appid": "246620", "steamid": "profiles/76561197963933537", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593604800.0} {"text": "A megfelel≈ë korral rendelkez≈ë sz√°m√°ra aj√°nlom. A sok pozit√≠vumot nem soroln√°m, ink√°bb csak egy negat√≠vumot. Sokszor kell kis t√©ren √°thaladva harcolni, amit nehez√≠t az ilyen helyzetben j√≥l haszn√°lhat√≥ fegyver effektje, alig l√°tni t≈