 being my favourite cars to run. The game uses an upgraded Rfactor engine with great physics and more livly graphics and textures. Clearity @High FPS and any resoloution is always awesome. The modeling is pretty great. If you can't play anyone online, then why not just get together with a friend and race the Ai Together, it works for me. This is so much better then all those other games that pass them selves off as simulation, such as Asetto Corsa, and Project DLC. All super cars, no soul. The server system finally works, the Hud is pretty good for such an old game engine, and the controls are solid, just make sure you spend enough time tuning the wheel outside and inside the game and make sure the steering feels just right.", "appid": "431600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198050045314", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480593600.0} {"text": "io ke ze no zoi jueko", "appid": "335300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198087111557", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1458734400.0} {"text": "Many game modes very fun", "appid": "240", "steamid": "profiles/76561197996523120", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1521979200.0} {"text": "Very fun with friends! The QoL changes make Monster Hunter feel fresh and fluid", "appid": "582010", "steamid": "profiles/76561198048504421", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575201600.0} {"text": "–ü—Ä–æ—Å—Ç–æ –Ω–∞—É—á–∏—Å—å –∏–≥—Ä–∞—Ç—å –∏ –Ω–µ —Å–ª–∏–≤–∞—Ç—å –∏–≥—Ä—ã.", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198166517116", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479988800.0} {"text": "good but hard", "appid": "248570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198235819668", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561723200.0} {"text": "screm :)", "appid": "773920", "steamid": "profiles/76561198131493690", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1544097600.0} {"text": "Kinda fun , even in non prime matchmaking , keep your good work valve , and improve the VAC system to make this game better and better :)", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198876146770", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1551441600.0} {"text": "Not a big fan of Tomb raider series still after playing for like 4-5 hours or so here are some pros and cons :) ‚Ä¢ Absolutely gorgeous world to explore especially in wide-open areas, dense beautiful environments and hub areas with impressive designs. ‚Ä¢ Puzzles and Challenge Tombs in particular are fantastic, amazingly designed and satisfying to solve. ‚Ä¢ Character moments resonate, gets deep into Lara‚Äôs character and continues to be a strong well acted heroin. ‚Ä¢ Optimization is Average as long there is no ray tracing. ‚Ä¢ Great music which matches the ambient of the game. ‚Ä¢ Photographer mode which has quite a few features but still far from perfect. ‚Ä¢ Pretty much bug and glitch free expect some texture pop up in some scenes. ‚Ä¢ Story-line isn‚Äôt really told that well fails to capitalize on past game‚Äôs characters and story much of the story feels contrived, or full of holes. ‚Ä¢ Narrative is weak, disjointed and throwaway, noticeably sub-par voice acting in some scenes. ‚Ä¢ Platforming sometime feels imprecise which is frustrating. ‚Ä¢ Stealth feels inconsistent and unsophisticated. ‚Ä¢ Combat isn‚Äôt that great, mechanics feel clumsy and unsuited to most encounters. Game is set to release after few hours today. I would recommend waiting for sale. Running unstable 50-60fps@High Gtx 970.", "appid": "750920", "steamid": "profiles/76561198244372940", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created":