 will get). It's incredible quite how immersed you manage to get in this - it's Story-wise, come on, let's not kid ourselves here, it's a fully fledged Half-Life game. The story isn't emotional at all, but it's incredibly riveting. Only a few amount of important characters, with no specific antagonist except for just \"The Combine\" TM, but the intricacy of the HL-universe is enough to get you hooked in. I'd never played another HL game before this, but that really doesn't matter. Gameplay is incredible. Puzzles are original and interesting; not so difficult that you have to be smart to solve them, but they're not total 'gimme's either. Most of them play off the same few mechanical tricks, but in interesting ways that require you to genuinely stop and think about what you're trying to accomplish. In terms of combat, they really hit the nail on the head here. Controls feel natural, even in the heat of battle, and the guns play super well into this. Perfect execution on the items like grenades or medkits. 10/10, best VR game ever", "appid": "546560", "steamid": "profiles/76561198100112667", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602417600.0} {"text": "great game much buy so play very greatness", "appid": "72850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198070177879", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1389268800.0} {"text": "This is the greatest comeback of gaming history. Other devs need to learn from HG's example. Hello Games is still updating this game. Look at the release date. If you are reluctant , visit", "appid": "275850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198103396111", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574942400.0} {"text": "Russisch lernen leicht gemacht wusste ich garnicht das Valve jez auch spachkurse macht", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198002022808", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_f