robably notice with the first few characters but seems to have improved over time. Game only has 1 song that loops forever and will probably annoy you into muting it fairly quick. The game tries to make itself seem witty and funny with the store page descriptions but eh. I dropped the game quite a while ago since it was pretty repetitive. Although I can't speak for whatever the \"phone flings\" content is since I have not seen it, but having limited time characters sounds sounds a bit iffy to me and moreso since I believe you have the option to pay for said limited time characters if you missed them (correct me if i'm wrong). There are microtransactions aplenty which shouldn't be surprising since it's a f2p game, but be warned that it has lots of time saving pay 2 not play stuff which seems silly since computer clock cheesing exists. Last time I played, they had limited time pinup images to unlock occasionally where you just logged in daily with the option to pay if you missed any days. If you're interested, check it out but I don't think the game is too special. Unless you want to quickly just cheese the whole thing by setting your computer clock forward to see all the content. Maybe clickers just aren't my thing.", "appid": "459820", "steamid": "profiles/76561198045655521", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "38", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602936000.0} {"text": "–ö–ª–∞—Å–Ω–∞—è –∏–≥—Ä–∞", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198216114519", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562155200.0} {"text": "YARRRRAM Gƒ∞Bƒ∞ OPTƒ∞Mƒ∞ZASYON VE YARRRRAM Gƒ∞Bƒ∞ GRAFƒ∞K VE YARRRRAM Gƒ∞Bƒ∞ OYUN. Single oynayacaksƒ±nƒ±z HARƒ∞KA", "appid": "251570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198871072380", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1566907200.0} {"text": "Battle Royale", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198053348060", "voted_up": fal