 premium subs. I feel bad about it. I bought LoA because it was F2P. A few weeks later they switched to subs. Personally I feel cheated. Sure, you don't have to do so but w/o you'll miss stuff in game (key aspects). Sorry, to me LoA is a waste of time and money in its current state.", "appid": "594770", "steamid": "profiles/76561198007173692", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "20", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1569153600.0} {"text": "It doesn't offer key configuration, so it's a problem for south paws like me. It's mostly Q, W, E, R, T, A, S, D and F. I gave it a try, because the game looks good and fun. However, demons defeated me several times when my right hand doesn't have a memory on the left side of the keyboard. It got on my nerves.", "appid": "233290", "steamid": "profiles/76561197993216595", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1597406400.0} {"text": "game bad", "appid": "335300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198039822988", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1583582400.0} {"text": "I really Like Need for Speed I really don't enjoy this one", "appid": "1222680", "steamid": "profiles/76561198039435818", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593345600.0} {"text": "Still a garbage game. They're pushing more microtransaction cosmetics over optimizing their game. This is why your game has mixed reviews, and it will continue to be like this if you ignore the community's opinions.", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198028274698", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1506772800.0} {"text": "–ú—ã–ª–æ –µ–±–∞–Ω–æ–µ –¥–∞–∂–µ –∑–∞ –±–µ—Å–ø–ª–∞—Ç–Ω–æ –Ω–µ —Å–æ–≤–µ—Ç—É—é –∏–≥—Ä–∞—Ç—å –≤ —ç—Ç—É —Ö—É–µ—Ç—É", "appid": "286570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198243571770", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "vote