470", "steamid": "profiles/76561197990698410", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1590148800.0} {"text": "15 Minutes was enough for me to uninstall the game. Great concept, reminded me a lot of Fantavision for the PS2 - but the music was so cacophonous that I was driven to distraction. If you're any way musically-inclined you may wish to steer clear, but if you're in it for the puzzles, just mute the game and play the game without the tunes - it doesn't suffer for it.", "appid": "207670", "steamid": "profiles/76561197997741024", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1580817600.0} {"text": "–Ω–µ —É–¥–æ–±–Ω–æ –∏–≥—Ä–∞—Ç—å –æ–¥–Ω–æ–π —Ä—É–∫–æ–π :DDD", "appid": "927890", "steamid": "profiles/76561198165288895", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574856000.0} {"text": "CZEMU TO JEBANE GOWNO SIE NEI ZAMYKA I MI BLOKUJA KURWA STEAMA JA PIERDOLE JEBANE SCIERWO NARZEDZIE NEI ZNAM ZADNEJ FAJNEJ GRY Z TEGO KURWA GOWNA JA PIERDOLE", "appid": "266310", "steamid": "profiles/76561198255808290", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1577620800.0} {"text": "Bu oyunu kesinlikle ve kesinlikle tavsiye etmiyorum sa√ßma sapan ceza sisteminden gƒ±na geldi artƒ±k a≈üƒ±rƒ± derece gereksiz haftalarca uzayan cezalar var oylama ile herkesin evet oyu vermesi √ºzerine takƒ±mƒ± trolleyen bi oyuncuyu attƒ±k √ºstelik bot olmasƒ±na raƒümen berabere kaldƒ±k buna raƒümen ma√ß bittikten sonra oyuncu attƒ±nƒ±z diye 1 hafta ban yedim sanki ben atƒ±yorum oyuncuyu adminim sanki ben o zaman oylama sistemi neden koydunuz sa√ßma salak hilecilerin oyunu zehir eden trollerin cirit attƒ±ƒüƒ± √ºstelik hi√ßbir ≈üekilde ceza almadƒ±ƒüƒ± bir oyunda hakkƒ±nƒ±zla oyun oynamak √ßok zor ger√ßekten bunlarƒ± g√∂r√ºnce insan oyundan soƒüumakla kalmƒ±yor intikam almak istiyor hile a√ßanlarƒ