rofiles/76561198225039708", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1564920000.0} {"text": "It has many bugs but it's an awesome and very funny game with a lot to explore and a lot to do. Definitively better with friends to play and enjoy. It also supports mods :) Totally recommended, but again, be aware of the bugs. EDIT: Had to change my review because the bugs have overtaken the fun of the game. It has been several times they released a patch and a couple of days later they had to release a hot fix because the ‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô• EVERYTHING. This time, they ‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô• mods up so much, that I can't add and/or remove any mod without my game crashing. I'm literally stuck. Btw, the game is not finished yet, the final boss still doesn't exist, you can't leave the exile and restart the game. The story itself is unfinished, but hey, they have released several 10$ seasson pass/DLC for you to dress and have new weapons and ‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô• if you want. I'm at the point where this ‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô• games is robbing me enough GBs to install a GREAT game, and honestly, I think that, instead of waiting for years for the devs to do their job and finish the game, I will just uninstall it and leave it as it is. The greed of the devs ruined the game, thy don't deserve my time anymore, and they deserve this review so MAYBE they realise what they are doing.", "appid": "440900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198039516329", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0} {"text": "Extremely easy tile puzzle game. The artwork is decently cute, reminding me of more old-school H games. My main problem is that moving the tiles isn't particularly smooth, and every so often a tile will get \"stuck\" out of position, meaning you have to close the game and restart the puzzle from the beginning. This game is cheap, but still not worth wasting your money on. It even has a cheat button to auto-complete the puzzles - you're better off just browsing Deviantart for free. EDIT// It doesn't seem to have the problem with the tiles getting stuck now, and I think this might have been an issue with my own operating environment!", "appid": "984750", "steamid": "profiles/76561198025566272", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1547985600.0} {"text": "its a fun game no doubt about that but after a while it gets ultra repetitive and a little bit boring as theres nothing new , the content is so so minimal and items in shops are the same almost every day , idk why a season should last all that long time just to struggle the same maps over and over again worst thing in the game is team games it seriously should be removed", "appid": "1097150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198300071758", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600603200.0} {"text": "Je≈ºel jeste≈õ fanem titan's quest'a, to jest to pozycja zdecydowanie dla Ciebie, w epoce Path of Exile jednak rozw√≥j postaci ala TQ wypada blado a zbieranie ekwipunku jest przyjemniejsze choƒáby w diablo.", "appid": "219990", "steamid": "profiles/76561197961924647", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1565265600.0} {"text": "Hi. Pros: - This game is great, is ‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô• perfect, after the patchs run very well. - The single player mode is funny, not as the MK9 history but is great. - Fight with friends is funny, i recommend it. - Predator and Jason character are awesome, but i miss something i can't remember right now. - Nice combo and fatalities. Cons: - This is important, Warner Bros ended his support to this game with less than 1 years from the game release, no more content(as DLC:Kombat Pack 2, only PS4 and One), no fixes for online(Yes for PS4 and Xbox one), no Goty edition(yes for PS4 and One). - Bad port on his release. - The on