ic is too beautiful. -The only problem that makes the game bad, is that the gameplay is too long and the process of taking resources to upgrade yourself and your mech(robot) that allow u to advance the story and new type of systems, planets and resources are too long. To advance in the story u should advance to a new type of systems(5 types) that contain new planets that require a new suit to survive, further each type of systems has new ores u need to mine to build new things and upgrade your mech. It just taking a loot of tiiiime, oh come on!!", "appid": "211820", "steamid": "profiles/76561198315440050", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1573819200.0} {"text": "Hate trilogy", "appid": "10", "steamid": "profiles/76561198818498753", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1604664000.0} {"text": "Such a masterpiece of a game sadly ruined by cheating kids!", "appid": "202990", "steamid": "profiles/76561198123281576", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1580126400.0} {"text": "This is a game with a message, and the message is BEWARE!. This is not a game for playing -- this is a game for uninstalling and avoiding. This game is only for those keen on regurgitation. I think ‚Äì no, I‚Äôm positive - that this is the most unattractive game I have ever played in my entire life. You know, in the short time I played this, this game demonstrated every loathsome characteristic of bad game design and even discovered a few new ones. It is visually repulsive, and intellectually retarded. Charging money for this is morally reprehensible, vulgar, insensitive, selfish, and stupid. The game has no purpose, a lousy sense of functionality and is broken in every sense of the word. I played Busby 3D, one of the worst platformers ever made, CortexGear:AngryDroids makes Busby 3D better, more enjoyable by just existing and