ame provides almost nooooo help at all. You have to look up where you MIGHT find materials, and this isn't even considering that you can get killed by players at any time. At the moment, I have the game and love, all it's flaws and all. But, I wouldn't recommend getting it yet, till it's at least out of early access.", "appid": "290080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198081258853", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1457352000.0} {"text": "Bir s√ºr√º bug var. Klavye ve fare tu≈ülarƒ±nƒ± deƒüi≈ütirmek √ßok sorunlu. Hikaye √ßok basit yani alt metni yok. T√ºrklere kƒ±saca ≈ü√∂yle diyebiliriz vuru≈ü hissi yok ^^. Bu oyunu oynamak zaman kaybƒ±. Bu oyunu es ge√ßin direk \"Resident Evil Revelations 2\" oynayƒ±n.", "appid": "222480", "steamid": "profiles/76561198397429538", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601467200.0} {"text": "love the efx lost head and legs. the game is not for alle and it's ‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô• sry to say", "appid": "629760", "steamid": "profiles/76561198167073446", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561723200.0} {"text": "cam greu jocul, nu se compara cu lol la controale si astea, aici iti trb skilluri reale :)", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198424230517", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593432000.0} {"text": "Better than World of Tanks, but with a confusingly similar name. High tier battles are utterly ‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô•‚ô• for balance. Nice WW2-era gameplay, though. My recommendation is to stay away, unless you're a serious AFV fan.", "appid": "236390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198072670107", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "I would not recomend this game to anyone. My first reason being that the controls are absolutly terrible